text: Lenggries (Bavarian: Lenggrias) is a municipality and a town in Bad Tölz- Wolfratshausen, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. It is the largest rural municipality in Bad Tölz-Wolfratshausen. == References == == Other websites == * Official Website of the Town (English) Category:Bad Tölz- Wolfratshausen Category:1250s establishments
